ve-episode series from the creators of the 2012 Game of the Year: The Walking Dead. Based on Fables (DC Comics/Vertigo), an award-winning comic book series, it is an often violent, mature and hard-boiled thriller where the characters and creatures of myth, lore and legend are real and exist in our world. As Bigby Wolf - The Big Bad Wolf in human form - you will discover that the brutal, bloody murder of a Fable is just a taste of things to come, in a game series where your every decision can have enormous consequences.", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 20, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 31, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 43, "name": "Mystery"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/the-wolf-among-us", "videos": [{"id": 1572, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "7a_St9DTuO0", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7a_St9DTuO0", "title": "The Wolf Among Us - Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7a_St9DTuO0/maxresdefault.jpg"}], "collections": [{"id": 2824, "name": "The Wolf Among Us"}], "characters": [{"id": 4438, "mug_shot": {"id": 3615, "url": "//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/egjunmhvkot1utmeafbn.jpg"}, "name": "Bigby Wolf"}, {"id": 4442, "mug_shot": {"id": 3670, "url": "//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/q2mtqr2uc0fcmtxi4eiw.jpg"}, "name": "Ichabod Crane"}, {"id": 970, "name": "Faith"}, {"id": 26, "name": "Colin"}, {"id": 666, "name": "Butcher"}, {"id": 4440, "name": "Mr. Toad"}, {"id": 4447, "name": "Bufkin"}, {"id": 4453, "name": "Georgie"}, {"id": 4459, "name": "\"John\""}, {"id": 4467, "name": "Jersey Devil"}, {"id": 4469, "name": "Tim"}, {"id": 4443, "name": "Grendel"}, {"id": 4456, "name": "Nerissa"}, {"id": 4458, "name": "Clever Hans"}, {"id": 4454, "name": "Bluebeard"}, {"id": 4460, "name": "Lawrence"}, {"id": 4465, "name": "Caller"}, {"id": 4466, "name": "Crooked Man"}, {"id": 4468, "name": "Dr. Swinehart"}, {"id": 4450, "name": "Cabbie"}, {"id": 4455, "name": "Jack Horner"}, {"id": 4457, "name": "V